===Noun===
'''dude''' (''Plural:'' [[dudes]])

#(''slang'') A man.
#(''slang''; ''used in the [[vocative]]'') Used as a term of address for a man.
#:''Relax, dude.''
#(''archaic'') [[dandy]], a man who is very concerned about his dress and appearance

